// sanitize test fixture — representative Public Suffix List rule kinds.
// Mirrors the real PSL's shapes so the wildcard/exception/IDN handling can be
// tested hermetically (no network). "ck" simulates the IANA single-tld entry
// combined with the PSL "*.ck" / "!www.ck" rules.

// normal rules (the suffix itself is a public suffix)
com
net
uk
co.uk
jp
cn
ck

// wildcard rules (any single label under the parent is a public suffix)
*.ck
*.kawasaki.jp

// exception rules (carve a name back out of a wildcard)
!www.ck
!city.kawasaki.jp

// IDN rule in U-label form (must match the A-label host)
公司.cn
